1. *Don* je bio samo mali deo velike slike. (Don was just a small part of the big picture.)

2. On se nada da će *don* uspeti da završi posao. (He hopes that he will be able to finish the job.)

3. Ona je *donela* svoju torbu. (She brought her bag.)

4. On je *donosio* novine svaki dan. (He was bringing the newspaper every day.)

5. Ona je *donela* knjigu sa sobom. (She brought a book with her.)

6. On je uvek *doneo* nešto novo. (He always brought something new.)

7. Ona će *doneti* obrok za ručak. (She will bring the meal for lunch.)

8. Ona je *donešena* u bolnicu. (She was taken to the hospital.)